{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819520/extras/Preview_1.gif?t=1657894324\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819520/extras/Welcome_to_Constellations.png?t=1657894324\" /><br>Constellation is a transformative relationship with constellations and puzzles, to discover something that only the stars hold. Take a comfy spot and enjoy this experience!<br><br>Increase mindfulness, concentration and focus through a conversation with the stars. Evade yourself from everyday life as you build constellations in the sky.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819520/extras/Preview_2.gif?t=1657894324\" /><br><br>Constellations is a meditative, minimalist puzzle game about finding patterns in the stars. In each level, connect the stars without the lines crossing and slowly fill the sky with constellations. Explore a starmap full of carefully designed levels with diverse mechanics, or go to the black hole to play endless puzzles.<br><br>Stars, constellations and figures can be found as main elements: Stars reveal the way to reach a sky completely made up of constellations. Some constellations reveal incredible pictures.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819520/extras/Preview_5.gif?t=1657894324\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819520/extras/Features.png?t=1657894324\" /><br>- Simple and intuitive puzzle mechanics for all ages.<br>- Polished controls for a satisfying experience.<br>- Meditative astronomic chill visuals and music.<br>- Solidly designed campaign with over 100 levels with varied mechanics.<br>- Level generator with infinite combinations.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store